query:
SELECT
                    MIN(l1_batch_number) AS "l1_batch_number!",
                    circuit_id,
                    aggregation_round
                FROM
                    prover_jobs_fri
                WHERE
                    status IN (
                        'queued',
                        'in_gpu_proof',
                        'in_progress',
                        'failed'
                    )
                GROUP BY
                    circuit_id,
                    aggregation_round
